  "title": "Platform Engineer (Middleware) / West / FMCG / 1 Year Contract",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Government link company in the FMCG industry. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Platform Engineer to be part of their IT team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the West – easily accessible.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Duties:</p><ul><li><strong>Middleware Architecture Design</strong>: Design and implement a scalable, robust middleware architecture to overcome integration challenges with fragmented systems and legacy infrastructure.</li><li><strong>System Integration Management</strong>: Develop and manage integrations between WMS, SAP, TMS, DBP, WES, and other systems to ensure seamless data flow and automation.</li><li><strong>Message Exchange & Security</strong>: Ensure secure, reliable message exchanges between systems using appropriate messaging protocols.</li><li><strong>Collaboration & Stakeholder Engagement</strong>: Work closely with business units, IT teams, vendors, and stakeholders to gather requirements and deliver effective solutions.</li><li><strong>Performance Monitoring & Optimization</strong>: Implement proactive monitoring, troubleshooting, and performance optimization to ensure efficient, scalable middleware operations.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Computer Science/IT or any relevant field</li><li>5 years of relevant experience in middleware system intgeration</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><strong>Email Address: tc1@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R21101676</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Ng Zhi Qing Alethea</p>",
